---
title: Sticky Plum Pork Bao Buns with Potato Fries & Oyster Sauce Greens
description: It’s that time again - get ready to bao down to flavour town! Tender pork loin is tossed in a rich plum sauce before being added to
fluffy, steamy bao buns. Served alongside much-loved potato fries and flavourful greens, this dish ticks all the boxes.
